  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/PackageDescription\/SupportedPlatform\/IOSVersion\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T20:13:42Z\n---\n\n# SupportedPlatform.IOSVersion\n\n**Structure**\n\nThe supported iOS version.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nstruct IOSVersion\n```\n\n## Type Properties\n\n- **v10**: The value that represents iOS 10.0.\n- **v11**: The value that represents iOS 11.0.\n- **v12**: The value that represents iOS 12.0.\n- **v13**: The value that represents iOS 13.0.\n- **v14**: The value that represents iOS 14.0.\n- **v15**: The value that represents iOS 15.0.\n- **v16**: The value that represents iOS 16.0.\n- **v17**: The value that represents iOS 17.0.\n- **v18**: The value that represents iOS 18.0.\n- **v26**: The value that represents iOS 26.0.\n- **v8**: The value that represents iOS 8.0.\n- **v9**: The value that represents iOS 9.0.\n\n## Supporting iOS\n\n- **iOS(_:)**: Configures the minimum deployment target version for the iOS platform.\n- **iOS(_:)**: Configures the minimum deployment target version for the iOS platform using a custom version string.\n- **iOS**: The iOS platform.\n\n## Conforms To\n\n- Sendable\n- SendableMetatype\n\n",
